title: The Weeknd, 'Uptown Funk' duo lead Soul Train nominations
text: > Entertainment The Weeknd, 'Uptown Funk' duo lead Soul Train nominations FILE - In this Aug. 30, 2015, file photo, Bruno Mars, left, and Mark Ronson accept the award for male video of the year for “Uptown Funk” at the MTV Video Music Awards in Los Angeles. The Weeknd and Mark Ronson and Bruno Mars are tied for five nominations each at the Soul Train Awards this year on Nov. 6. The show will air on Centric and BET on Nov. 29. (Photo by Matt Sayles/Invision/AP, FIle)
